<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                        unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan>
<expan>Lochn<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie ir in auf geistlich gerichte
                                <expan>gelad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, und
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Mollitor, wie ir in als von geistlichs
                        gerichtes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> manen <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt, und das sey <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als ir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> tumprobst czü handeln habt.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir sölich ladung und manung gen
                        den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> abtün und von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        geistlichen gerichte gen in lassen <add>wöllet</add>, das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Het ir
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czü in iht czesprechen, darumb
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                            <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czoge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>slewnige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim sind.
                            <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Oswaldi.</ab>
</div>
